# Vite dev-server env. Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored automatically by
# Vite) and set values per local setup. All vars MUST be prefixed `VITE_*`
# to be exposed to the client bundle — Vite drops anything else.

# WebSocket auth token. MUST match WS_SHARED_SECRET in backend/.env when
# that's set. Leave blank for dev (backend default-allows when its secret
# is unset). REQUIRED whenever the backend is exposed beyond a private
# dev laptop.
# VITE_WS_TOKEN=
